Module com.fy916.bubblebobble
Package com.fy916.bubblebobble.gaming.elements

Class ObjectFeature

java.lang.Object
com.fy916.bubblebobble.gaming.elements.ObjectFeature
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameObject
public class ObjectFeature extends Object
A superclass intended to show the basic feature of any object in the game. Includes the location and size of the object, and whether it can be removed.
Author:
fy916
